title: Living Foods Market
description: This 5,000 square foot market offers fresh organic and local produce and foods made by local producers; packaged food like organic chips, non-dairy ice cream, hard cider, tofu, and alternative flours; plus eco-friendly household products. The cafe is primarily non-veg but does make an assortment of prepared salads. Alternative milk option for coffee drinks and vegan/gluten-free pastry options available.
